FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our blockchain data analysis platform
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Blockchain analytics refers to the process of extracting insights from blockchain data. Our platform provides tools to monitor, analyze and visualize activity on various blockchains.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We currently support analysis for Bitcoin, Ethereum, Litecoin and several other major blockchains. New chains are added regularly based on demand.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: What kind of data can be analyzed?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: You can analyze transactions, addresses, smart contracts, token transfers and many other on-chain activities. Our platform also integrates off-chain data sources.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Who uses your blockchain analytics platform?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Our users include crypto exchanges, financial institutions, investigation agencies, blockchain startups and individual researchers analyzing blockchain data.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Sign up for a free trial to explore our analytics dashboards and API. Our documentation provides guides to import your own blockchain data and build custom analyses.

PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Blockchain Analytics App
ACCORDION_QUESTION_1: What is this app used for?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app provides in-depth analysis of new blockchain data and transactions as they occur. It helps track and monitor activity on various blockchain networks.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: Currently, our app supports analysis of Bitcoin, Ethereum, and several other major blockchain networks. We are continually adding support for more blockchains.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Our app connects to blockchain nodes and parses the latest blocks and transactions. Advanced algorithms identify patterns, anomalies, and insights from this data.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Is the app suitable for businesses?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, our blockchain analytics app is designed for enterprise use cases. It provides valuable intelligence for blockchain-based businesses, financial institutions, and investigators.
PAGE_DETAIL_1_VALUE: Our app continuously scans and analyzes new blockchain data as it gets added, giving you up-to-the-second insights.
PAGE_DETAIL_2_VALUE: Leverage our powerful analytics engine to uncover valuable patterns, trends and anomalies in blockchain activity.
PAGE_DETAIL_3_VALUE: Set custom alerts to be notified instantly when specific blockchain events or conditions are detected.
